{"tid":1150717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科技商機：人造肉之後　人造奶也登場！","createTime":"2019-05-12T05:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T12:38:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cdabd5a8a46447e5ec38152f0e1d315ab654b7a5","tid":1150717,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190510/photo/bkn-20190510175838215-0510_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190510220701\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190510%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190510175838215-0510_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190510220701&h=4e233c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，自從首家人造肉公司Beyond Meat剛剛在月初成功於美國納斯達克上市，公司周四收市最新收報68.27美元，較招股價25美元勁升1.7倍。有人造肉的完美示範，難怪市場分析即時指，同樣是人造而非母牛擠出的牛奶的人造奶，其潛在商機更廣，因為人造奶可添加更健康的原素。 <br />\n<br />\n全球經濟研究網站MishTalk的專欄作家Mike Shedlock在一篇文章中介紹更環保、更健康、更燒錢的人造奶。<br />\n<br />\n而在這一賽道上，目前已經擠滿雀巢、杜邦、巴斯夫等商業巨頭以及成百上千家初創企業。從美國硅谷到歐洲瑞士的實驗室，數億美元被用於研發生產與普通牛奶口味相同但所含蛋白質不同的人造奶（Bioengineer Milk）。 <br />\n<br />\n普通牛奶中87%是水，剩下的物質包括蛋白質、酶、脂肪、碳水化合物、維生素和礦物質等。而後者才是人造奶技術真正需要花功夫的地方。 <br />\n<br />\n在實驗室中，科學家依次通過把這些化學物質根據消費者需要放入試管中調試，並利用生物工程酵母來生產出真正的牛奶蛋白質，最終目的是複制出普通牛奶的口味，但同時可以更富營養價值。 <br />\n<br />\n人造奶最大的優勢在於更加健康。以母乳低聚醣為例，該物質能夠調節腸道菌群，預防腹瀉以及抗感染。最近世界衛生組織還發現，它還能防止嬰兒變得肥胖。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，人造奶也更有利於環保。每年約有3%的溫室氣體排放可歸因於乳製品生產。而如果全球停止消費奶製品合肉類，可以節省75%的耕種土地面積，省下的面積是美國加上中國、歐盟、澳洲那麼多。如果人造奶真的被市場接受，那上述功勞都可以被記在其名下。 <br />\n支持者還表示，人造奶還可以解放奶廠的牲畜，避免它們受到不必要的虐待。 <br />\n<br />\n從全球液態奶產業的角度看，人造奶有機會成為一個攪局者。但是它的對手除傳統牛奶外，還有近年來被時尚健康人士推崇的植物蛋白奶，特別是燕麥奶。 <br />\n<br />\n現時，除了最主流的杏仁奶、豆奶和椰奶，還出現了藜麥蛋白飲料、山核桃蛋白飲料、米漿、榛子奶、亞麻籽奶等等。其中，杏仁（64%的市場份額）、大豆（13%的市場份額）和椰子（12%的市場份額）仍然是植物蛋白奶的主流，但燕麥奶增速明顯。 <br />\n<br />\n人造肉之後，人造奶也登場了。以美國為例，數據顯示，過去一年內美國燕麥奶銷量大漲近50%，而植物奶市場整體銷量增幅僅為9%，傳統牛奶銷量更是下跌2.8%，脫脂牛奶跌幅甚至達到16.5% 。 <br />\n<br />\n可口可樂旗下牛奶品牌Fairlife今年發布了2%降脂超濾牛奶，號稱富含DHA Omega-3成分，對各年齡段的消費者的身體都很有好處，尤其利於腦健康。"},{"pid":"5264ebf18b4033e102c9389142dae8dac0edaf38","tid":1150717,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190510/photo/bkn-20190510175838215-0510_00842_001_02p.jpg?20190510220701\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190510%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190510175838215-0510_00842_001_02p.jpg%3F20190510220701&h=163d9578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人造奶加入不同的植物種子，如杏仁、榛子等等，令其營養力大增，銷路上升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190510/mobile/bkn-20190510175838215-0510_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190510%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190510175838215-0510_00842_001.html&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNWwFhK%2BZ0PNwQmNlOVL%2F21oE%3D&h=1f65a000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190510/mobile/bkn-20190510175838215-0510_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d6ea6df6f8d5d342f4a4c607868dca8263151810","tid":1150717,"uid":250905,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"人造奶一早就有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e02dc55b782be7b294d07edb48ffb37d485d15","tid":1150717,"uid":137506,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:26:34.000Z","msg":"假㗎啲奶！"},{"pid":"8aa9eb87a7d1e24763f9e8174315ed4ba53fe528","tid":1150717,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bc509c01567ae228db4ad3d348f2554cf43005","tid":1150717,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"乳糖不耐症嘅福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6da3a0751f98f44d400fce9017846979cc6e3a","tid":1150717,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:57:16.000Z","msg":"呢D係太空科技,好岩太空發展用"},{"pid":"8b97afb8b278dafadbeff3d4fbd3b04d64e6c496","tid":1150717,"uid":130568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d6ea6df6f8d5d342f4a4c607868dca8263151810","tid":1150717,"uid":250905,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"人造奶一早就有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:01:18.000Z","msg":"先前蝗國先有節目即時用化合物合成奶<br />\n再合成士多啤梨奶昔"},{"pid":"16b3fbe3efb99ab5df5fcb6a7283d14622e87341","tid":1150717,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"我想要個人造靚女"},{"pid":"dbc16a98ce6c53bb8386821956bac4c505c8b6ff","tid":1150717,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"複制出普通牛奶的口味不如複制出普通人奶的口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ddba12ec93da2c3b899cba8a9cbdf2d75210df","tid":1150717,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:37:55.000Z","msg":"人根本唔應該飲其他生物嘅奶"},{"pid":"f2423a031501b55219e191701cffb6c243bf3ca3","tid":1150717,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69bc509c01567ae228db4ad3d348f2554cf43005","tid":1150717,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"乳糖不耐症嘅福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:40:12.000Z","msg":"依家都有冇乳糖牛奶啦"},{"pid":"94931e4e6fbc1aac6c40ac82c40fc8106a66798b","tid":1150717,"uid":151257,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/025859_4a79c1983ced3779ef1b6e3f13dba8c9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F025859_4a79c1983ced3779ef1b6e3f13dba8c9.gif&h=7c59c1e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fab26c7c5ae3cc095dc398e30f4a9f7a5ca3ff7","tid":1150717,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"機界原種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1536cf6888d39f0822cc3f00cd2b5fa98e851d","tid":1150717,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:45:16.000Z","msg":"人奶咪人造既奶囉"},{"pid":"332c3b8e6fa21aea0b7e34d3b11eb2c6061f2689","tid":1150717,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:50:17.000Z","msg":"舊野啦，支那玩左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國去年爆發黑心奶粉導致多名嬰兒死亡和「大頭娃娃」後遺症的事件，近日大陸媒體又踢爆許多牛奶竟是從廢棄的皮鞋、皮衣、皮箱中提煉出水解蛋白，然後加入各種化學添加劑製成。媒體同時透露，在生產過程中，不乏一些專家為賺取暴利從旁「輔導」黑心廠商。<br />\n<br />\n《新民周刊》報導，假牛奶的製造方法令人匪夷所思，根本不需要與「牛」發生任何關聯，只要用香精、糖、自來水和一些添加劑，就可以造出假牛奶來。甚至一雙破皮鞋經過一番處理後，也可變成假牛奶的原料。 <br />\n<br />\n提煉皮革蛋白當原料<br />\n<br />\n中國奶業協會理事王丁棉指出，不肖業者用城市垃圾裡的破舊皮衣、皮箱、皮鞋，還有廠家生產沙發、皮包等皮製品的廢料，經過化學、生物技術處理，水解出皮革中原有的蛋白，取代牛奶中的天然蛋白。他說：「有人專門收購這類工業垃圾，有人專門生產水解蛋白，這項技術很容易掌握，成本並不高，農民從一些專家手中買到技術，用什麼藥劑，怎樣的程序，這些都有專家指導。」<br />\n<br />\n上海奶業協會副秘書長顧佳升表示，水解蛋白製成的假牛奶副作用很大，衛生、營養均不達標準，毒性反應是一個慢性發作的過程，兒童長期飲用後果堪憂。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，在一些不肖專家從旁指導下，牛奶造假的技術近年大幅精進。在一九九○年以前，造假者多在奶源上做手腳，譬如在鮮奶中摻水；但在一九九五年後，往鮮奶中摻牛尿、劣質豆粉、化肥只能算是「小兒科」，一些廠商一斤奶加兩斤水，將牛奶大量稀釋，然後倒入各種添加劑，硬將產品成分湊到國家規定標準。 <br />\n<br />\n用添加劑調配色香味<br />\n<br />\n近兩年來情況更為猖狂，這些不肖的黑心商人開始用完全與牛奶毫無關係的物質造奶。令人納悶的是，這些製造假牛奶的小工廠負責人多是農民出身，教育水準低，甚至是文盲，他們如何取得這些造假技術？ <br />\n<br />\n一名業界人士則透露，所有的配方都是從專家手中流出的，「如果沒有一些專家的輔導，他們即使養一百年牛、一千年牛，也造不出足以逼真的假牛奶。」 <br />\n<br />\n王丁棉痛批這些「專家」是「可恥的叛徒」。他說：「他們為賺取外快，將專業技術轉賣給農民企業主，甚至專門為不法廠商量身訂做造假配方。」一些專家則利誘業者：「你要發財就來買我的專利，我教你如何使用，用各種添加劑調配，就把牛奶的色香味全都解決了。」 <br />\n<br />\n藥粉調製也能做假奶 <br />\n<br />\n王丁棉憂心忡忡地表示，現在已經出現專門的藥粉，只要用水按比例來調配，就可以變成逼真的假牛奶，危害消費者身體健康。 <br />\n<br />\n皮革含毒劑難清除<br />\n<br />\n「皮鞋變牛奶」是以皮革廢料、毛髮等為原料，加入石灰、鹽酸、雙氧水等工業原料，透過預處理、水解、脫色、濃縮、乾燥等程序，可提取動物蛋白，一般是用於動物飼料的添加劑，黑心廠商則以此取代牛奶所含的乳蛋白。<br />\n<br />\n但因皮革製造過程多使用重鉻酸鉀或重鉻酸鈉等有毒物質，這些化學物質滲入皮革很難清除；用皮革生產水解蛋白，有毒物質殘留產品中，最後被人體吸收而中毒，危害很大。 <br />\n<br />\n皮鞋變牛奶製程<br />\n<br />\n「皮鞋牛奶」是利用化學方法製造程序，將皮革的蛋白質轉換為類似牛奶的蛋白質，再混充天然牛奶出售。<br />\n<br />\n製造程序如下：<br />\n1.從城市垃圾堆中收集破舊皮衣、皮箱、皮鞋，以及廠商生產沙發、皮包剩下的皮革剩料。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfFS3Eu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfFS3Eu.png&h=098091aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.經過化學、生物技術處理，水解出皮革中所含的蛋白。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kAeXvjF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkAeXvjF.png&h=24b952da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.將人造水解蛋白加入各種添加劑，提高產品口感。"},{"pid":"7350cb1e5fa2f11a523d82582b7419d3acf49013","tid":1150717,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2423a031501b55219e191701cffb6c243bf3ca3","tid":1150717,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69bc509c01567ae228db4ad3d348f2554cf43005","tid":1150717,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"乳糖不耐症嘅福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:40:12.000Z","msg":"依家都有冇乳糖牛奶啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:15:35.000Z","msg":"標榜冇乳糖嘅牛奶仲要係常溫包裝唔係間間超市有賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766ec182b82eb55662861b6b31df17528bcf175b","tid":1150717,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}